- Each unresolved dimension now shows exactly 3 proposals + `Other / new opinion`.
- Proposal custom IDs include action/run/revision/dimension/option identity, e.g. `minerva:v2:select_proposal:<run>:r1:dscope:oa`.
- Selecting A/B/C resolves only that dimension and advances to the next.
- `Other` routes to dimension-specific freeform input without lowering ambiguity.
- Updated CLI interaction choices, gateway plugin rendering text, tests, and minimal docs.
